sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KServeCtrl as kserve-controller-manager
    participant LLMCtrl as llmisvc-controller-manager
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>Python Init Container
    participant CloudStore as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Gateway as Gateway / Istio<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EPP as Inference Scheduler<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IGRouter as InferenceGraph Router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,CloudStore: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate & Validate<br/>TLS (OpenShift serving cert)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admitted (defaults applied)
        K8sAPI-->>KServeCtrl: Watch event: InferenceService created
        KServeCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment + init container spec<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Note over StorageInit,CloudStore: Init container phase
        StorageInit->>CloudStore: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCS SA / Azure / HF Token
        CloudStore-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts to emptyDir volume
        KServeCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        KServeCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute / VirtualService / Ingress<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        KServeCtrl-->>K8sAPI: InferenceService status: Ready
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,Predictor: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Disaggregated Serving
        User->>K8sAPI: POST LLMInferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate & Validate (v1alpha2)<br/>TLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admitted
        K8sAPI-->>LLMCtrl: Watch event: LLMInferenceService created
        LLMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment / LeaderWorkerSet<br/>+ scheduler + routing sidecar
        LLMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute + InferencePool
        LLMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ScaledObject (KEDA)<br/>+ OTelCollector
        Note over Client,Predictor: Inference request path
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS
        Gateway->>EPP: Forward request<br/>HTTP in-cluster
        EPP->>Predictor: Route to vLLM decode pod<br/>HTTP in-cluster
        Predictor-->>EPP: Prediction result
        EPP-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Client,IGRouter: Flow 3: InferenceGraph Request Routing
        Client->>IGRouter: Request to graph endpoint<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
        IGRouter->>Predictor: Step 1: InferenceService A<br/>HTTP 80/TCP in-cluster
        Predictor-->>IGRouter: Result A
        IGRouter->>Predictor: Step 2: InferenceService B (transform)<br/>HTTP 80/TCP in-cluster
        Predictor-->>IGRouter: Result B
        IGRouter-->>Client: Combined/routed response
    end
